        "shadowOpacity": 127,
        "smoothed": true,
        "underlined": false,
        "text": "Stage 1 — Break the Head\n\nThe Worm attacks mostly with sudden head strikes, lunging forward to bite or slam the ground.\nAvoid the attacks and use your dash to strike its head. Each successful dash damages the boss.\nRepeat this pattern while staying mobile and avoiding its bites.\n\nStage 2 — Rampage\n\nThe Worm enters a rampage state. It becomes immune to damage and begins to lose health over time as its body destabilizes.\nDuring this phase, the Worm moves more violently and attacks more frequently.\nFocus only on dodging and surviving until the rampage ends and the boss weakens.",
